      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">There is a need to establish well-defined, public safety scenarios
                for the evaluation of current and future communication technologies for first
                responders. The scenario descriptions must contain enough details to be considered
                representative of key public safety operations and their communications needs. The
                purpose of this document is to provide guidelines for developing these so-called
                'public safety scenarios'.</abstract>
